    <title>Star Wars Outlaws gets a new trailer — and PC hardware requirements</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="A screenshot from Star Wars Outlaws, showing the main character, Kay Vess, riding a speeder bike." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/90EdtFn-hw-soaagga36EhhDnqI=/114x0:1337x815/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73529219/Star_Wars_Outlaws.0.png" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;Image: Ubisoft&lt;/figcaption&gt;
    &lt;/figure&gt;

  &lt;p id="JIF2qt"&gt;Ubisoft has published the PC requirements for &lt;em&gt;Star Wars Outlaws,&lt;/em&gt; which is releasing later this month on August 30th, in a &lt;a href="https://ubisoft.pxf.io/c/482924/864200/12050?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ubisoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fgame%2Fstar-wars%2Foutlaws%2Fnews-updates%2FI6lWJ2gpUJAQD9oj731rB%2Fstar-wars-outlaws-pc-specs-and-features-revealed&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;post&lt;/a&gt; that also points to a &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pDs2t5vSFp0&amp;amp;t=4s"&gt;new gameplay trailer&lt;/a&gt; for the &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/23758235/star-wars-outlaws-gameplay-trailer-ubisoft-forward-2023"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Grand Theft Auto-&lt;/em&gt;style space adventure&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="OQkAsh"&gt;The trailer compares the game’s looks when certain features, like DLSS, are turned on versus off. There may not be any major revelations in terms of story or gameplay here, but it could give you an idea of whether you want to upgrade anything for the game or not.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div id="AGOiBe"&gt;&lt;div style="left: 0; width: 100%; height: 0; position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p id="4cweVI"&gt;On the hardware side, &lt;em&gt;Outlaws&lt;/em&gt; seems fairly forgiving of PCs still using components like the GeForce GTX 1660 GPU or Intel Core i7-8700K CPU. &lt;a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/ubisoft-shares-star-wars-outlaws-full-pc-requirements"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Eurogamer&lt;/em&gt; notes&lt;/a&gt; that you’ll need DLSS or FSR to run the game at minimum specs. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="YltyGA"&gt;From Ubisoft’s page: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p id="QPiX4m"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Minimum &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="F96Vyw"&gt;• Visual...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
