      &lt;img alt="An F1 car driving on a track, with a crowd behind it." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/JjLLeClPdk1AbEiwnPYtFass6a4=/0x0:5602x3735/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73529144/2158299651.0.jpg" /&gt;
